sources.title: Sharknado: Heart of Sharkness | Full Movie | Mockumentary
sources.description:
Sharknado: Heart of Sharkness - A 'mockumentary' about David Moore, the filmmaker who first dreamed of "sharks in a tornado" and brought on disaster by using real sharks. The first SHARKNADO was to be a movie never seen, a crime never reported, a tale never told. Until now.
2015.  Stars: Jared Cohn, Zack Ward, Julie McCullough
